*openvpn-2.0 (29 Apr 2005)

  29 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  -openvpn-1.1.0.ebuild, -openvpn-1.3.1.ebuild, -openvpn-1.3.2.ebuild,
